07:12.000 --> 07:14.240
is this not quite that equivalent?

07:14.240 --> 07:17.120
It seems to be the way that all the other services go.

07:17.120 --> 07:19.720
There's a little bit here, and then this little bit there,

07:19.720 --> 07:21.920
and then you get the shutdown notice.

07:21.920 --> 07:22.720
