23:28.160 --> 23:30.000
when you came back initially, you came back

23:30.000 --> 23:33.480
as advertiser-based, but then eventually transitioned

23:33.480 --> 23:36.600
to member-only after your readers said, do it, we'll pay.

23:36.600 --> 23:41.000
